      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is the perfect blank canvas for someone looking for a rewarding restoration challenge. While it currently requires significant mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its prime, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a classic model at a budget-friendly price. If you have the tools and the passion, this car is ready for a total transformation!",
