      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows absolutely zero signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster thanks to a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating, with no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, featuring a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is clean, and the staggered performance tires are mounted on wheels with zero curb rash. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
